data.description: Amazing opportunity for this awesome Paloma Lake 3 car garage home! Open, bright, and beautiful! This 3 bedroom plus flex room that could easily be a 4th bedroom. Assumable FHA loan under 3%! Ask listing agent more and look in the documents section. The location in the neighborhood is perfect!  Close to the pool and the in neighborhood elementary school, and Settlers Park is less than a 1/2 mile!  Enjoy all that this area has to offer with a beautiful, well taken care of home. The quality just oozes the moment you walk in the front front door with the natural light from the entry skylight.  The 3rd car garage allows for plenty of space for hobbies, wood working, cars, or just additional parking.
